Name: Ornamental Jewel with Engraved Dancer
Description: The rectangular ornamental jewel is completely flat. It is decorated with an engraving of a dancer in motion, playing a tambourine. She wears loose clothes that reveal her breast and legs. The folds of the dress, which fly in all directions behind her back, are rendered with amazing precision. Her face is round and featureless, with no details shown except for a little part on the top of her right eye.
